<section class="application-form">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="application-box">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div class="head-text">
                            <h3>Admission 2018</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="head-text head">
                            <h4>Admission Process</h4>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accardion-box">
                            <ul>
                                <li class="active">
                                    <p class="head">
                                        <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>Documents
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p>Below documents should be scanned and sent to us.</p>
                                        <ul class="list">
                                            <li>Passport</li>
                                            <li>School certificate</li>
                                            <li>Bachelor Diploma / Master Diploma (if available)</li>
                                            <li>Transcript</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <p></p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="head">
                                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>invitation letter
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p>
                                            After application process is started, we get the invitation letter in about one week. As soon as an
                                            invitation letter is ready, we send hard copy of it to the applicant via DHL. Applicant should pay
                                            99$ (invitation letter fee) and courier service fee in advance.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="head">
                                        <i class="fab fa-cc-visa"></i>visa application
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p>List of the documents required to obtain visa for study in Ukraine:</p>
                                        <ol class="list">
                                            <li>
                                                A completely filled in visa application form per each passport holder – dated and personally signed
                                                by the applicant. Visa application registration and making an appointment at the consular section
                                                of the Embassy for submitting visa application packages must be made through the web-site:
                                                <a href="http://visa.mfa.gov.ua">http://visa.mfa.gov.ua</a>
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                Birth certificate (legalized and officially translated into Ukrainian) and three ordinary copies
                                                of it.
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                Medical certificate (legalized and officially translated into Ukrainian) and three ordinary copies
                                                of it.
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                School certificate (legalized and officially translated into Ukrainian) and three ordinary copies
                                                of it.
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                Valid health insurance with coverage of at least 30,000 EUR or equivalent in other currency, unless
                                                otherwise stipulated by legislation or international treaties of Ukraine. When multi-entry visa
                                                is requested, availability of health insurance valid for the first intended visit to Ukraine shall
                                                be considered. Holders of diplomatic or service passport shall be exempt from this requirement
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                A bank statement to confirm sufficient financial means for the period of intended stay in Ukraine
                                                – for 90 days and return to the country of origin or transit to a third country or guaranty to
                                                obtain sufficient financial resources in Ukraine. When multi-entry visa is requested, financial
                                                sufficiency for the first planned visit to Ukraine shall be considered. Holders of diplomatic or
                                                service passport shall be exempt from this requirement
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                2 color photos seized 35 mm x 45 mm- recent, passport-sized, resembling applicant’s travel document
                                                photo.
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                A national passport, valid for at least three months after the expiry date of the requested visa
                                                and it must contain at least 2 spare visa designated pages, must be issued no more than ten years
                                                ago;
                                            </li>
                                            <li>Copy of the first page of the passport.</li>
                                            <li>
                                                A bank receipt confirming the payment of the consular fee + its copy (payments must be made through
                                                any branch of ARAB BANK, by a directive of the consular employee of the Embassy after he checks
                                                your application package).
                                            </li>
                                        </ol>
                                        <p>
                                            <span>Note:</span> In case of necessity the Embassy can require additional documents which confirm the
                                            purpose of visit to Ukraine.
                                        </p>
                                        <p></p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="head">
                                        <i class="fas fa-plane"></i>applicant arrival
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p>
                                            We arrange the date of arrival and prepare temporary apartments or hostel for applicant in advance.
                                            <br>We will pick-up applicant from airport and transfer to temporary apartment
                                            <br>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="head">
                                        <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i> tuition free
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="text">
                                        <p>
                                            After arriving to Ukraine, applicant will sign a contract with University, proceed tuition fee via
                                            local bank and get all needed documents and information to start his/her classes.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-form">
                            <p>You can check you invitation letter’s authenticity below</p>
                            <div class="letter-number">
                                <span>Invitation letter number:</span>
                                <input type="text" placeholder="xxxxxx">
                            </div>
                            <div class="birthday-date">
                                <span>Your birth date:</span>
                                <input type="date" placeholder="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="button">
                                <div class="btn-demo">
                                    <a href="">Check</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="head-text head">
                            <h4>Application Form</h4>
                            <p>
                                Fields marked with an
                                <span class="clr-red">*</span> are required
                            </p>
                        </div>
